---
title: Turkey Cutlets with Garlic-Sage Gravy plus Mashed Sweet Potatoes, Candied Pecans & Brussels Sprouts
description: Looking for a quick “all-in-one” Thanksgiving dinner? Try this delicious meal that hits every holiday note. Center stage are juicy turkey cutlets drizzled with velvety homestyle garlic and sage gravy. On the side are roasted Brussels sprouts and smooth, buttery mashed sweet potatoes topped with candied pecans to complete this festive feast.
